change_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ID"               AS "ID",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ObjectID"         AS "ObjectID",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."Time"             AS "Time",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."Attribute"        AS "Attribute",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."OldValue"         AS "OldValue",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."NewValue"         AS "NewValue",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ChangedBy"        AS "ChangedBy",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."OperationID"      AS "OperationID",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."OperationType"    AS "OperationType",
    "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ExecutionType"    AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "c_o_custom_PurchaseDocument" AS "PurchaseDocument_Changes"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_PurchaseDocument" AS "PurchaseDocument"
        ON "PurchaseDocument_Changes"."ObjectID" = "PurchaseDocument"."ID"
WHERE "PurchaseDocument"."DocumentCategory" IN ('Standard PO')

property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    "PurchaseDocument"."ID"                                                           AS "ID",
    "PurchaseDocument"."CreatedBy_ID"                                                 AS "CreatedBy",
    "PurchaseDocument"."Vendor_ID"                                                    AS "Vendor",
	"PurchaseDocument"."CreationExecutionType"                                        AS "CreationExecutionType",
    "PurchaseDocument"."CreationTime"                                                 AS "CreationTime",
    "PurchaseDocument"."Currency"                                                     AS "Currency",
    "PurchaseDocument"."PaymentTerms"                                                 AS "PaymentTerms",
	"PurchaseDocument"."DocumentCategory"                                             AS "DocumentCategory",
    "PurchaseDocument"."DocumentType"                                                 AS "DocumentType",
    "PurchaseDocument"."DocumentTypeText"                                             AS "DocumentTypeText",
    "PurchaseDocument"."PurchaseOrganization"                                         AS "PurchaseOrganization",
    "PurchaseDocument"."PurchaseOrganizationName"                                     AS "PurchaseOrganizationName",
    "PurchaseDocument"."PurchaseDocumentNumber"                                       AS "PurchaseDocumentNumber",
	"PurchaseDocument"."IsCanceled"										              AS "IsCanceled",
    "PurchaseDocument"."SourceSystemInstance"	                                      AS "SourceSystemInstance"
FROM "o_custom_PurchaseDocument"  AS "PurchaseDocument"
WHERE "PurchaseDocument"."DocumentCategory" IN ('Standard PO')
